cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.DB, cs.DC, cs.LG 

This paper deals with the privacy and security of a cryptocurrency, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data analysis and mining of the Monero blockchain, which could be categorized under databases (cs.DB) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper proposes countermeasures to improve privacy, which could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and cryptography (cs.CY).
